ion":2,"to":260.18},{"content":"兄弟齊心 奮發努力才行啊","from":260.52,"location":2,"to":264.23},{"content":"真是煩人的蟲子","from":269.37,"location":2,"to":271.45},{"content":"這麼說","from":272.29,"location":2,"to":273.26},{"content":"清盛那傢伙已經魂不守舍了？","from":273.44,"location":2,"to":276.84},{"content":"是","from":277.02,"location":2,"to":277.38},{"content":"(藤原基房：殿下爭道事件當事人。此時已卸任攝政，轉任關白。)","from":277.38,"location":2,"to":278.15},{"content":"已經成了一個尋常的痴呆老頭啊\n(藤原基房：殿下爭道事件當事人。此時已卸任攝政，轉任關白。)","from":278.15,"location":2,"to":281.31},{"content":"這真乃天賜良機","from":283.03,"location":2,"to":285.97},{"content":"你說後白河法皇？","from":301.08,"location":2,"to":302.92},{"content":"是","from":303.23,"location":2,"to":304.01},{"content":"他沒收了重盛長子維盛繼承的越前領地…\n(越前國：在琵琶湖之北，面向日本海，今福井縣及石川縣一帶。)","from":304.4,"location":2,"to":309.5},{"content":"此前盛子掌管的藤原家家產 也遭沒收了","from":311.49,"location":2,"to":317.78},{"content":"這段時間","from":320.21,"location":2,"to":321.53},{"content":"他又對朝廷的人事安排頗多置喙","from":321.72,"location":2,"to":326.1},{"content":"這混帳","from":326.88,"location":2,"to":328.26},{"content":"父親？","from":329.75,"location":2,"to":330.93},{"content":"竟敢自行其是","from":331.43,"location":2,"to":334.1},{"content":"父親！","from":334.66,"location":2,"to":335.72},{"content":"父親…","from":336.89,"location":2,"to":337.75},{"content":"父親…","from":339.08,"location":2,"to":340.52},{"content":"宗盛 出兵","from":343.03,"location":2,"to":344.84},{"content":"為父也要回京","from":346.59,"location":2,"to":348.15},{"content":"為父還沒老呢！","from":350.23,"location":2,"to":352.49},{"content":"速速讓路 速速讓路","from":360.56,"location":2,"to":362.59},{"content":"是清盛大人","from":362.59,"location":2,"to":363.62},{"content":"他是要報復朝廷啊","from":363.62,"location":2,"to":365.62},{"content":"父親 您可算回來了","from":370.27,"location":2,"to":372.69},{"content":"宗盛","from":377.93,"location":2,"to":378.64},{"content":"在","from":378.64,"location":2,"to":379.18},{"content":"知盛","from":379.5,"location":2,"to":380.2},{"content":"在","from":380.2,"location":2,"to":380.76},{"content":"重衡","from":380.86,"location":2,"to":381.61},{"content":"在","from":381.61,"location":2,"to":382.17},{"content":"即日起","from":383.4,"location":2,"to":384.43},{"content":"將攝政關白及以下的四十三人解職","from":384.72,"location":2,"to":389.04},{"content":"今後 皆由我平家族人擔任","from":390.04,"location":2,"to":393.42},{"content":"特別是收取重盛領地的關白基房","from":394.18,"location":2,"to":398.03},{"content":"將那傢伙流放日向國\n(日向國：在今九州島西南。)","from":398.68,"location":2,"to":401.4},{"content":"出陣了 快走 快走！","from":402.14,"location":2,"to":404.74},{"content":"-速速開門 -從那包抄","from":408.72,"location":2,"to":410.67},{"content":"-全都抓起來！ -休要抵抗！","from":410.8,"location":2,"to":413.15},{"content":"-別放跑了！ -饒命啊！","from":413.15,"location":2,"to":415.0},{"content":"臣已出家 還望免去流放日向之刑啊","from":415.41,"location":2,"to":419.89},{"content":"既如此 就改為流放備前吧","from":420.46,"location":2,"to":424.13},{"content":"宗盛","from":424.62,"location":2,"to":425.42},{"content":"在","from":425.42,"location":2,"to":425.92},{"content":"你去見法皇陛下 請他移居鳥羽離宮","from":426.11,"location":2,"to":432.07},{"content":"您要幽禁法皇陛下？","from":432.86,"location":2,"to":434.6},{"content":"若真把事做絕…","from":434.6,"location":2,"to":436.11},{"content":"是！孩兒這就去辦！","from":436.92,"location":2,"to":439.19},{"content":"連我也要？","from":443.56,"location":2,"to":445.28},{"content":"平家武士竟敢反噬我等主君！","from":447.6,"location":2,"to":451.81},{"content":"絕不饒你 絕不饒你 清盛！","from":455.33,"location":2,"to":459.44},{"content":"八尺鏡 天叢雲劍 八尺瓊勾玉","from":479.14,"location":2,"to":484.43},{"content":"此三神器 乃是天子之證","from":484.68,"location":2,"to":489.24},{"content":"你可是歷代天子中 繼位時最年少的","from":489.52,"location":2,"to":493.41},{"content":"這不是年少 而是太過幼小吧","from":493.58,"location":2,"to":495.89},{"content":"德子 你應該更高興些才是啊","from":496.31,"location":2,"to":498.9},{"content":"你的兒子 我的外孫當天皇了","from":499.25,"location":2,"to":503.33},{"content":"對不對？","from":503.44,"location":2,"to":504.16},{"content":"你看 他也知道這是喜事","from":506.75,"location":2,"to":509.52},{"content":"另外…","from":510.98,"location":2,"to":512.08},{"content":"高倉上皇陛下","from":514.03,"lo